# Task 9 – Add Fields to Borrow Request Table

## Project

Smart Library Request Workflow in ServiceNow

## Description

This task configures the Borrow Request (u_borrow_request) table by adding the fields required to manage book borrowing requests.

## Fields Added

- Requested By (Reference → User [sys_user])
- Book (Reference → Book [u_book])
- Request Date (Date/Time)
- Status (Choice)

## Status Choices

- Requested (Default)
- Approved
- Rejected
- Returned

## Steps Performed

1. Opened the Borrow Request table.
2. Added Requested By reference field.
3. Added Book reference field.
4. Added Request Date field.
5. Added Status choice field.
6. Configured Status choices.
7. Set Requested as the default value.
8. Verified all fields on the Borrow Request form.

## Expected Outcome

The Borrow Request table is fully configured to store, manage, and track student borrowing requests.

## Technologies Used

- ServiceNow
- System Definition
- Dictionary Entries
- Reference Fields
- Choice Fields

## Status

Completed
